Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a businessman's town. I snuck in somehow by graduating from a state college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get my ass kicked by my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you yearn to be like that just to get by in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of winter, where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all that seems far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's in front of me is the azure of the South China Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clamoring wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right Mr. Japanese, I'm going to ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one package you got from Asahi Industries in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you're in charge of until you hand it over to the chief in Borneo. This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I want to ask is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's everything we were going to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, this is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him in his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll start singing like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one disk is more than enough for the payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Payment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you through yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone heading straight for us from Supick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a scout from the Filipino Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic Benny-Boy, everything's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to disperse and then you'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the deal's off if anyone decides to come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see there is a torpedo launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be blown out of the water, then stay still for the next half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting relaxed over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan is getting further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Lagoon to Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart jobs are lovely, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trade-off goes as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connect me to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigational Department Chief Kageyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the case we have been informed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the situation to you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today at 4pm the Burgenbiria Trade Company contacted us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...regarding the negotiations for the disk stolen from the Meramarsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Russian Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front for the group that aims to take top position after displacing the Chinese Mafia from Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they after specifically? Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely the route to Southeast Asia where the barter is going to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wish to take part in some of our more unsavory trade routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful, having something to be blackmailed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they do not seem to know what's really on the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out it will be the worst scandal since the founding of Asahi Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A report from Jakarta has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to a local Chinese merchant, the Russian Mafia has yet to receive the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disk is still in the hands of the pirates that attacked the Meramarsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't trust the word of the Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must take the disk before it reaches them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it reaches them? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. The board will leave this matter in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing what actions to take will also be your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, what do you plan on doing with the hostage? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This job is twenty grand! Only twenty grand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong about collecting a bonus with a ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be killed, Benny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to negotiate with Japan? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have their phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a bank account to accept the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just kill his ass and throw him in the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't damage the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch. Dutch, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, so let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive. I don't know why, but I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right. Let's go topside for a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll contact your company somehow and set up a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ransom, huh? This'll go on my permanent record.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have our own priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting the disk to the client comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just delivery boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brush up against the law from time to time, so we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what they call the Stockholm Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I feel like this big guy next to me is the only one I can trust in this whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima Rokuro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of that employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okajima, Director. Okajima Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is entirely the fault of my managerial skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only informed recently, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because there were no other employees we could trust with vital information,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was some time lost in communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an opinion, Kageyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company is in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot accept any more delays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The E.O. Company, with whom we've made a secret contract, have already sent their mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I feel bad for this employee. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okajima, Director. Okajima Rokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he means you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere to get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I was a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where on Earth is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a pistol on every table?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Western movie bar, at the end of the World?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was started by the losers of the Vietnam War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They started taking in deserters too and before we knew it, it went to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hookers, junkies, mercs, killers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irredeemable criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you dislike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese pubs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love those unguarded smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up or I'll throw you out onto the beach. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not suited for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have that kind of face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, I'm going to make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being around him for two years all I know is that he's tough, intelligent and weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on trying to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A college in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with fire pissed off the Mafia and the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved his ass before he was used as a weight in a suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this worthless storytelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not old enough to be reminiscing about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One for you, one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way here for a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's talk about something a littler cooler, Mr. Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beer's as good as piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you drink, you don't get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man you'll drink rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if... you're a wuss who can't even take a challenge from a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll make you wear a skirt, put on ribbons and take you to a dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate chugging down drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're forced to drink at company socials. Don't mock a Japanese businessman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring all the Bacardi you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I thought you didn't like fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't trust Asahi Industries' response.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I left out bait, and a Chinese rat bit. I'm talking to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's on the move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're owner's name loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinginan's Wan Taikei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wan Taikei sent an assassin to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sent an assassin to Roanapur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the number and affiliation of those soldiers. Hurry, we're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys from Extra Order, a mercenary contracting agency! I don't know how many there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The E.O. Company scouts experienced war junkies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just our luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For god's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give any runners extra assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure there are only corpses when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, if they are your friends then you deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've bulletproofed the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can handle up to a .50 caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miraculously, I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally graduated a state college and got into a good company!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to enjoy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll end up wasting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Show them why you're named Two-Hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em, Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you destroyed my shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll weld your asshole shut and make you a new one on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, at this rate, trading you is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we didn't make any plans to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we just part ways here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't pull our leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, you war junkies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, Bao was so pissed he looked like a steaming pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we pay him back he's going to weld our assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary. Makes me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lot more entertaining than Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, 16 dead, 8 wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry sir. We thought they were punks and underestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shutorm, they're not punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're somebodies we can go after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we had to shoot at were old men and brats in Liberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow and no fight left in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these guys are full of fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay at this speed we'll be at the Balawan Port by daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet Balalaika there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Rock,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny is getting in touch with your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pull it off if you try, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If negotiations don't go well, we're going to have to leave you around Malaya. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are bandits all around, but you shouldn't die immediately. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You bring me this far and you're going to let me die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! After dragging me all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least take me somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you cry then you want to use us like a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can show you what color your brain is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're using an Assault Dial so it's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, it's your boss, Kageyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Department Chief! It's Okajima, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the disk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That disk no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the situation, I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to explain, but we were hired to help develop nuclear capabilities for a certain country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disk contained the plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukes in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And war...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually I will be at the top and do something about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this can't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okajima-kun, for the sake of the 50,000 employees of Asahi Industries, disappear into the South China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be promoted to chief and we won't treat you badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the president and everyone under him will be at your funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professional ruffians should almost be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's my equipment status?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fully equipped, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockets and machine guns, the more you shoot the more the invoice will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese are very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were ditched pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sympathize, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ransom bonus is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that enough to make you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something coming straight at us over the ocean, but it's not a boat, it's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 3 hours 5 minutes. Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A low-altitude assault gunship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An assault helicopter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to see them, I can smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them. Using that to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun?! Don't make me hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be more than a comfort, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming. He's on our ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good, not good. This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, it's not good, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You try it, dipshit Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding under a torpedo launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You impotent son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to suffer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're just gonna watch from up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, we can turn them into mincemeat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From their heads to their tails, they're in my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to laugh at them while they cry, howl and piss themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do and say whatever you want to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, even the Department Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to suffer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that.
